node.text:
Happy Earth Day!

Thank you to everyone who shared their amazing creative suggestions with @wyliecaudillart last week. In honor of #EarthMonth, Wylie painted an incredible triple-vignette mural that will certainly impress you. Watch the entire creative process - and tell us what you think of the final reveal!

Should we invite Wylie to paint another mural? If so, comment and share your ideas!

#SHLTR #EarthDay #EarthDay2021

node.text:
The Historic Modern by @modernvenicehomes is a California cottage revived with a modern touch, located in Venice. The front portion of this 1907 one-story, Craftsman bungalow was relocated from an adjacent site and paired with the respectful two-story edition that introduces modern materials, such as metal siding and large glass windows. With the utmost attention to detail, the architecture and interior design embrace maternity without disrespecting the cottage's historic roots and neighborhood character. 🏡

Click the link in our bio to learn more about this unique development by M.E Development Inc., @jba_interiordesign, and @abramsonarchitects - and what's next in store for this collaboration. Photos by Laure Joliet.
